high_descs: Turn around and go to the black table.
Grab the candle that is sitting on the black table.
Back up and move to the left so you are at the center of the table.
Place the candle on the table in front of the toilet paper.
anns.task_desc: Move the candle to a different location on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room.
Pick up the candle from the back end of the bath tub.
Turn left and stand in front of the black desk.
Put the candle down in front of the toilet paper.
anns.task_desc: Move the candle from the bath tub to the desk next to the toilet paper.

high_descs: Turn around facing the side table and go towards it.
Pick up the table on the side of the tub.
Turn to the left and walk to the edge of the table. Turn to the right facing the black table.
Sit the candle on the table in front of the toilet paper.
anns.task_desc: Move the candle from the tub to the table.
